data.description: Interest rate buy down offered from Shane Patterson of Lending Hand Mortgage! Contact listing agent for details. Nestled off the charming drive of Greenbrier Cemetery Road, this beautiful 5.59-acre property presents a rare opportunity to enjoy the privacy and quiet of your own slice of country living with the ability to have your own ready-to-go workshop. Driving down the winding private entrance through the front tree line, the property opens up to reveal a charming tudor cottage style home with a drive-in basement, large front covered deck, and a spacious detached workshop already equipped with car lift, and everything you need to get to work!  1901Sqft in basement space ready to be finished out for what you need!
